title: World of Warcraft - Wrath of the lich king WOTLK-EU
description:
ISO copy of the game. i think it can be unpacked and installed from harddrive. if that doesnt work just mount it with f.ex Daemon tools :)

EU version of the game. It is not a beta!

The game is NOT playable unless you purchase the game and get a authentication Key.

The upload is ment to save time on install for those of you who are running to the stores at 00:01. The installation takes about 1 hour and you need to have the necessary patches in the wow folder. Make sure you have them so you don't have to wait additional 2 hours on patchdownloading :)
